"Elimination of D-arker Elimination Requ:
"Hey partner, I need your help...
OK, so I took a bunch of D-arker elimination requests
from Lavere but the amount requested is
unusually large so I'm having trouble.
What's more, even if you beat some weak hostiles
they won't accept that....
I need your help partner!　Even if it's just a for a little bit,
would you lend me hand?
*Hostiles of Lv. 47 or higher"

"あ、相棒、助けてくれぇー……
実はラヴェールさんって人からダーカー討伐
の依頼を受けたんだけど、頼まれた数が
尋常じゃなくてどうにも困ってんだよ。
しかも、弱っちいヤツだけ倒してきても
認めないなんて言うし……
頼む相棒！　ちょっとだけでいいんだ
手伝ってくれないか！

※Lv.47以上のエネミーが対象"
